    "materials_text": "MATERIALS\n Platinum Hot Start PCR Master Mix (2x) Thermo Fisher Scientific Catalog #13000014 \n twin.tec PCR Plate 384  Eppendorf Catalog #951020729 \n epMotion Reservoir 10 mL Eppendorf Catalog #0030126521 \n ep T.I.P.S 1 - 50 \u00b5L w/filter Eppendorf Catalog #0030015215 \n PCR Clean Water Contributed by users \n(1) ep T.I.P.S. Motion Racks 1- 50 \u00b5L w/filter\n(1) epMotion reservoir 10mL\n(3) twin.tec PCR Plate 384\nPlatinum Hor Start PCR Master Mix 2X",
