    "steps": [
      {
        "id": 671056,
        "guid": "8AEAB780C74111E8BF2B03AB3E97EDFD",
        "previous_id": 0,
        "previous_guid": null,
        "section": "Mix reagents",
        "section_color": "#A492FF",
        "section_duration": 0,
        "is_substep": false,
        "step": "In a sterile 10mL reservoir, add 2,534\u00a0\u03bcl of Platinum Hot Start PCR 2X Master Mix and 3,295 \u00b5L of PCR Clean Water per set of 384 samples\n 2534 \u00b5L, 2X PCR Master Mix 3295 \u00b5L, PCR Clean Water \nMix pipette. \n\n",
        "data": null,
        "protocol_id": 16448,
        "case_id": 0,
        "critical_ids": "",
        "duration": 0,
        "original_id": 0,
        "number": "1",
        "cases": [],
        "critical": null
      },
      {
        "id": 671066,
        "guid": "93E00AF0C74311E8BF2B03AB3E97EDFD",
        "previous_id": 671056,
        "previous_guid": "8AEAB780C74111E8BF2B03AB3E97EDFD",
        "section": "Setup epMotion automation platform",
        "section_color": "#94EBFF",
        "section_duration": 0,
        "is_substep": false,
        "step": "\n epMotion 5075 (Liquid Handling, Eppendorf, 5075000962) \nFollow the diagram below while setting up the epMotion worktable.\n\n[Capture3.PNG]](https://content.protocols.io/8bz3mm6.png) \nPlace (1) box of 1-50\u00b5L epT.I.P.S. w/filters on deck slot A4\nPlace empty 384 PCR Primer Plates 1-3 on deck stols B1-B3\nPlace 10mL reservoir with PCR Master Mix in the first slot of the reservoir rack, then place reservoir rack on deck slot B4.\n\n",
        "data": null,
        "protocol_id": 16448,
        "case_id": 0,
        "critical_ids": "",
        "duration": 0,
        "original_id": 0,
        "number": "2",
        "cases": [],
        "critical": null
      },
      {
        "id": 671069,
        "guid": "5B8DF160C74511E8BF2B03AB3E97EDFD",
        "previous_id": 671066,
        "previous_guid": "93E00AF0C74311E8BF2B03AB3E97EDFD",
        "section": "Execute automated protocol",
        "section_color": "#FFED92",
        "section_duration": 0,
        "is_substep": false,
        "step": "Remove box lids and execute protocol.\n\n(Protocol must be imported to epBlue software prior to attempting to execute it. _epBlue 40.6 or later_)\n [Application_3XPCR_mastermix aliquot 4ul_384eppendorf_181003_105306.export6](https://content.protocols.io/8b23mm6.export6)\n\nThe automated protocol transfers 4.6 \u00b5L of PCR Master Mix into (3) 384-well PCR plates using the multidispense feature of the epBlue software. ",
        "data": null,
        "protocol_id": 16448,
        "case_id": 0,
